videos.headline: App State strikes first with 46-yard TD
videos.description: Appalachian State strikes first as Zac Thomas connects with Christian Wells in stride on a 46-yard touchdown pass as they take a 7-0 lead over Arkansas State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (App State strikes first with 46-yard TD) 2020/10/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harrington easily dashes to 55-yard App State TD
videos.description: Daetrich Harrington takes the handoff and gets to the outside as he makes his way down the field to easily score a 55-yard touchdown as Appalachian State retakes the lead 14-7 over Arkansas State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Harrington easily dashes to 55-yard App State TD) 2020/10/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jones sneaks in for Arkansas State TD
videos.description: Jamal Jones takes the handoff and cuts his way up the middle as he slips through for an eight-yard Arkansas State touchdown to tie the game at 7-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jones sneaks in for Arkansas State TD) 2020/10/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mike Evans stretches out to make App State TD grab
videos.description: Mike Evans stretches out to make the catch to score a five-yard touchdown and extend Appalachian State's lead to 21-7 over Arkansas State. (edited)

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mike Evans stretches out to make App State TD grab) 2020/10/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: App State picks off Jeff Foreman's pass in the end zone
videos.description: The Red Wolves attempt a double pass and fail as Jeff Foreman throws an interception into triple coverage in the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (App State picks off Jeff Foreman's pass in the end zone) 2020/10/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Antonio Fletcher reels in acrobatic INT for Arkansas State
videos.description: Antonio Fletcher makes an unbelievably acrobatic grab as he reaches over his teammate and still manages to come away with the interception for Arkansas State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Antonio Fletcher reels in acrobatic INT for Arkansas State) 2020/10/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lincoln Pare gets to the outside for 48-yard Red Wolves' TD
videos.description: Lincoln Pare changes directions and reaches the sideline as he makes his way into the end zone for a 48-yard Arkansas State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lincoln Pare gets to the outside for 48-yard Red Wolves' TD) 2020/10/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thomas jukes his way to 60-yard App State TD
videos.description: Zac Thomas avoids Arkansas State defenders as he jukes his way down the field to score a 60-yard Appalachian State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Thomas jukes his way to 60-yard App State TD) 2020/10/22 ESHEET
